high_descs: Turn right and go to the bathtub.
Pick up the red towel to the right of the drain.
Turn around and walk to the sink behind you.
Place the red towel in the sink nearest you.
Open the right cabinet beneath the sink and pick up the red towel on the shelf.
Place the towel in the sink above the first.
anns.task_desc: Place two red towels in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and face the bath tub.
Pick up the cloth from the bath tub.
Carry the cloth and turn around to move to the sink.
Place the cloth in the sink.
Open the bottom cabinet and pick up the cloth.
Place the cloth in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two clothes to the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight to the tub.
Pick up the red rag in the tub.
Turn right and walk to the sink to your right.
Place the rag inside the sink.
Open the cabinet underneath the sink and remove the rag from it.
Place the rag beside the other rag inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two rags in the sink.
